title: The Pets Table - Air Dried Medium Box 1 x 3Lb Chicken & 1 x 3Lb Beef
description: Gently Air-Dried dog food cooked at low temperatures to preserve the essential nutrients. A healthy, tastier alternative to kibble which is delivered straight to your door and can be conveniently stored in your pantry. Made in the USA, with the world’s finest ingredients. All recipes are developed with vets and are AAFCO complete and balanced for all life stages and all sizes. Made with 100% real, whole ingredients. No artificial flavors or fillers. Supports improved digestion, healthier skin, shinier coats, immunity and increased energy levels. Feeding & transition instructions included within your delivered box. Roughly 3 weeks of food for a 30Lb adult dog. This medium variety box includes 3Lbs of Chicken & Sweet Potato & 3Lbs of Beef & Berries. *Your order will ship separately in The Pets Table branded box and may not arrive on your scheduled weekly HelloFresh delivery date (shipping is included in the total price). Customization of bundles is not available at this time.

